p.k: When Skip’s cousin arrives to watch him play a game in the park, he annoys everyone with his bad jokes! Until, Skip finds his cousin the perfect job… / After Mordecai and Rigby accidentally defrost a caveman, they try to civilize him so he can stay at the park. / Mordecai and Rigby stain Mr. Maellard's expensive White Stallion limousine while eating meatball subs for lunch, and go to drastic measures to get a new limo / Mordecai offers to give Margaret a ride to the airport, but runs into trouble with a technophobic street gang along the way. / Mordecai and Rigby get in a fight over Margaret and Mordecai sends them through time by destroying all the clocks.
